data.name: lblStepsAdmission.Text
data.value:
Step 1: Log in or register to begin your admission process.
Step 2: After logging in, the first thing you will see is the Admission Status page, where you can check the status of your admission.
Step 3: Next, fill out the application form and attach the required documents for admission.
Step 4: Once you have successfully completed the application form, proceed to pay the examination fee and select your preferred examination date.
Step 5: Wait for your scheduled examination date, and on that day, take the entrance examination.
Step 6: Finally, wait for the Notice of Admission (NOA). Once you receive it, you can move on to the next step, which is enrollment. Thank you!
